init_text: When you're 28, science discovers a drug that stops all effects of aging, creating immortality. Your government decides to give the drug to all citizens under 26, but you and the rest of the “Lost Generations" are deemed too high-risk. When you're 85, the side effects are finally discovered.

Your government decides to give the drug to all citizens under 26, but you and the rest of the “Lost Generations" are deemed too high-risk. When you're 85, the side effects are finally discovered.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This supplement, known as the "Immortality Pill" was a great success, and soon became a global phenomenon.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: However, the drug had a side effect that was not mentioned in the original advertisements.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The world had become a place of stagnation.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: In the year 2224, a new drug was created.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: and they wanted to prevent that from happening again.
